animeTitle: Genei wo Kakeru Taiyou: Fumikomenai Kokoro
animeDescription: Unaired 14th episode of Genei wo Kakeru Taiyou, broadcast on Nico Nico and included in the 4th Blu-ray and DVD volumes. It shows Akari and Fuyuna's lives prior to the main series as well as how Luna got started as a magical girl.
